node.text: It’s ok to fail, it’s ok to go through hard and trying times, it’s ok that life isn’t perfect. The key is to not stay in the area of funk and doubt. Lift yourself up and keep fighting! What doesn’t kill you will make you stronger! 💪🏽 comment and tag 2 friends!

node.text: It’s been a year since I released my book “My Truth” and the connection that I have made with so many people through it has been unreal. When I wrote this book I was in a dark, yet optimistic place. I was in search of healing and changing unhealthy patterns in my life. Along that journey of growth and learning This book was therapy for me. Putting my life out there, not for sympathy but it in hopes that it reaches those who may need the words inside of it. The steps I took to heal issues within me. Steps I took to transform my mind. Steps I took to recreate a newer, better version of myself. If you have gotten a copy of My truth, I pray it brought the healing you were looking for. If you haven’t gotten a copy yet they are available on Amazon, Barnes and Nobles and all other reading platforms. I am also happy to see all of the people reading my 31 day affirmation book. It’s crazy how speaking positive affirmations on a daily will bring a new found peace and blessings like never before! That book is also available on Amazon and all other reading platforms. I read everyone’s messages about how my books have touched you in some way and I am forever grateful!! I can’t wait to get started on my next book. Until then, Enjoy “My Truth” and “My Time is Now” love you all 🙏🏽 drop a comment if you have gotten one of the two or both. 🖤
